headline: Select Medical (SEM) Surpasses Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Select Medical (SEM) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +27.78% and +2.87%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Cigna Stock Tumbles on Margin Warning for Pharmacy Benefit Services
summary: The company said that profit margins for its pharmacy-benefit-services division would slide over the next two years.

headline: Cigna Beats Earnings Expectations. The Stock Is Facing Political Uncertainties.
summary: Cigna has outperformed peers as the managed-care industry faces policy challenges. Affordable Care Act subsidies are set to expire and premiums for next year are up 26%.
